data.description: Welcome to the ever popular and desirable community of King Oak Villas conveniently located in Saint Cloud close to shopping, restaurants and public transportation. This community does not allow rentals, so all the units are owner occupied. The community features 2 swimming pools and a cabana, located close to the bus line, restaurants, and shopping. This two-bedroom two bath villa features a living dining combo, eat in kitchen with a pass through to the dining area. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet. The unit also has a large screen enclosed, covered, lanai with ceramic tile flooring and a storage shed, where you will find hurricane shutters. Don’t miss out on this Villa. Schedule your tour today!
